17. axb5 $1 {As a rule, whenever Black play e5 we take on b5, the point is that Black has the positional threat of closing down the queenside with b4.} (17. Ra2 {allows the positional idea of b4.} b4 $13) 17... axb5 18. g3 $14 {We improve our position.} *

